Class AddPlayerCommand

    Command

    public class AddPlayerCommand
extends java.lang.Object
implements Command
    Class uses command pattern to abstract Add Country to Map Data. This class can be called by either the GUI or the command line to perform AddCountry to MapData * 
      *   AddCountryCommand command
  *     = new AddCountryCommand(new MapData(), new String("nigeria"), new String("africa"));
  *
